{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"908fba92b9","title":"复林伯渠电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b7103d9699","index":0,"year":1938,"month":8,"day":16,"articleId":"908fba92b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"b0e4f99ee9","name":"张闻天","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"00a5c97e96","type":"paragraph","text":"复林伯渠电\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"908fba92b9"},{"id":"92e63921a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年8月16日）在谈判中请坚持所提三个条件：一、陕甘宁边区区域为二十三个县：二、人员由国民政府正式委任：三、每月津贴十万元。谈判中心是区域问题，各县都须是完全的。[1]1938年8月12日，林伯提在西安致电毛泽东、洛南（张闻天）、陈绍（王明），周恩来、博古（泰邦宪）：蒋鼎文今日早上说，行政院认为院甘宁边区问题可由陕西省就近解决，边区至多只能划十七个县。我拟根据原来所提的三项条件交涉。这是毛泽东和落菌（张闻天）复林伯电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"908fba92b9"}],"page":{"id":"da2131eae1","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"908fba92b9","start":423,"end":423}}}},"__N_SSG":true}